title: THE MONTHLY THROW UP: TIM HENDRICKS
description:
Clean composition, bold lines, one badass Samurai -- It's no wonder legendary tattoo artist Tim Hendricks has been so influenced by Japanese art and print making. Listen to Tim talk about his inspiration for the piece, and what Japanese art has meant to him and many others in this month's TMTU.

Video: YB
